{
  "text": "A few complications after stent graft treatment were reported [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Rebleedings due to the dislodgment of stent grafts have been reported but most of them occurred within a day [CITATION_4] . We experienced delayed bleeding at 40 days after stent graft treatment. Thus, one should be aware of this complication, and careful observation after stent grafting with infection is recommended.",
